Expérience
General Manager
OTD Oncology Therapeutic Development

déc. 2008 - aujourd’hui 16 ans 8 mois

Clichy

Responsible for the planning, coordination and management of all business operations to achieve corporate goals. I am specialized in the development and implementation of business strategies for our partnering collaborations, with more than 20 years of experience in the executive management of CROs focused on preclinical and clinical drug development.

CEO
Early Drug Development Group (E2DG)

janv. 2016 - août 2023 7 ans 8 mois

Région de Paris, France

E2DG team is seeking out highly innovative translational projects in oncology. We are interested in the development of promising R&D projects, from the preclinical proof of concept to their early clinical development.
E2DG helps your business to open up the potential of your lead, bridging technical and scientific data with financial and strategy challenges.


Chief Financial Officer
Cvitkovic & Associés Consultants SA

mai 2000 - mars 2008 7 ans 11 mois

Le Kremlin Bicêtre

I bring with me over 15 years of experience in accounting and tax solutions. My strenghts are in control and management systems to ensure rapid development of technology companies. These included Cvitkovic & Associés Consultants SA, a Clinical Research Organization company focus on clinical development in oncology.

Auditor
FFP Fiduciaire Financière de Paris SA

févr. 1994 - mars 2000 6 ans 2 mois

Paris

I started my career as Auditor, for 6 years in a chartered accountant firm in Paris.

